Package rmi

Contains principal interfaces of the project.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Message
    Represents the message that is exchanged between sites.
    Site
    Represents a node of network
    SiteAdministration
    Represent a objet on each computer to manage the number of site by computer.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MessageImpl
    Is the implementation of the interface MessageTree.
    SiteAdministrationImpl
    Is the implementation of SiteAdministration contain a number which can be increment or decrement and provide the number of site on the same computer (rmiregistry)
